      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. It has been meticulously preserved, showing no signs of wear inside or out, and remains in perfect mechanical order with all original features functioning flawlessly. For a buyer seeking a car that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory, this is the perfect specimen.",
