      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits an impeccable exterior finish paired with a pristine, smoke-free interior that retains its original factory luster. Mechanically superior and rigorously vetted, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a showroom-quality asset. Every detail, from the precision of the panel alignment to the integrity of the drivetrain, confirms its status as a premier-tier offering. We invite rigorous inspection to verify its peerless condition.",
